item.title: Gallery Post
item.description: ths is a Gallery Post try As usual, a new post entry after a while. Much has changed since the last one, and I’m so super happy where I’m at right now. Me and my husband (yes, husband! Still weird to say it), finally reached my birth country: Italy; where he finally met for the first time my lovely and supportive family! We then decided to get married … I know right?
